			<note xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" place="foot" n="4" xml:id="foot_3" coords="2,105.24,727.01,108.49,8.37"><p>http://www.lemurproject.org</p></note>
			<note xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" place="foot" n="5" xml:id="foot_4" coords="2,105.24,736.51,228.47,8.37"><p>http://snowball.tartarus.org/algorithms/dutch/stemmer.html</p></note>
			<note xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" place="foot" n="6" xml:id="foot_5" coords="3,105.24,722.76,407.87,8.37;3,90.00,732.22,377.28,8.37"><p>The data for VideoCLEF 2008 has been provided by The Netherlands Institute of Sound and Vision (Beeld &amp; Geluid). Thank you also to the University of Twente for providing the speech recognition transcripts.</p></note>
		</body>
